Release 0.2-0:
  * Fixed solaris error.
  * Fixed rchk warnings.
  * Fixed hash table warning nightmare on very recent gcc versions.
  * API change: doc_counts() and readability() now accept nthreads argument.
  * Added function sylcount.nthreads().

Release 0.1-0:
  * Added readability().
  * Added sylcount().
  * Added doc_counts().
